admin:
Route::get('column', 'ColumnController@list')->name('admin.columnList')->middleware(['permissions:ColumnList']);    //栏目列表
        Route::get('column/{id}', 'ColumnController@detail')->name('admin.columnDetail')->middleware(['permissions:ColumnDetail']);    //栏目详情
        Route::post('column', 'ColumnController@create')->name('admin.columnCreate')->middleware(['permissions:ColumnCreate']);    //创建栏目
        Route::post('column/{id}', 'ColumnController@edit')->name('admin.columnEdit')->middleware(['permissions:ColumnEdit']);    //保存栏目
        Route::post('column/destroy/{id}', 'ColumnController@destroy')->name('admin.columnDestroy')->middleware(['permissions:ColumnDestroy']);    //删除栏目
        Route::get('article', 'ArticleController@list')->name('admin.articleList')->middleware(['permissions:ArticleList']);    //文章列表
        Route::get('article/{id}', 'ArticleController@detail')->name('admin.articleDetail')->middleware(['permissions:ArticleDetail']);    //文章详情
        Route::post('article', 'ArticleController@create')->name('admin.articleCreate')->middleware(['permissions:ArticleCreate']);    //创建文章
        Route::post('article/{id}', 'ArticleController@edit')->name('admin.articleEdit')->middleware(['permissions:ArticleEdit']);    //保存文章
        Route::post('article/destroy/{id}', 'ArticleController@destroy')->name('admin.articleDestroy')->middleware(['permissions:ArticleDestroy']);    //删除文章
notValidatedApp:
Route::get('column', 'ColumnController@list')->name('client.ColumnList');    //栏目列表

        Route::get('article/column/{id}', 'ArticleController@list')->name('client.articleList');    //文章列表
